{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Label placement relative to its geometry."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnsymbolstylelayer\/symbolplacement"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"symbolPlacement","fragments":[{"text":"symbolPlacement","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNSymbolStyleLayer(py)symbolPlacement","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"symbolPlacement"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/symbolPlacement"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSExpression","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"symbolPlacement"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is an expression that evaluates to "},{"code":"point","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Set this property to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to reset it to the default value."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of the following:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Constant "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNSymbolPlacement"},{"text":" values","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Any of the following constant string values:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"point","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":": The label is placed at the point where the geometry is located.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"line","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":": The label is placed along the line of the geometry. Can only be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"used on ","type":"text"},{"code":"LineString","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Polygon"},{"type":"text","text":" geometries."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"line-center","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":": The label is placed at the center of the line of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"geometry. Can only be used on "},{"code":"LineString","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Polygon"},{"type":"text","text":" geometries. Note that"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"a single feature in a vector tile may contain multiple line geometries."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Predefined functions, including mathematical and string operators","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Conditional expressions","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Variable assignments and references to assigned variables"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Step functions applied to the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"$zoomLevel"},{"type":"text","text":" variable"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property does not support applying interpolation functions to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"$zoomLevel"},{"type":"text","text":" variable or applying interpolation or step functions to feature"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"attributes.","type":"text"}]}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNSymbolStyleLayer":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer","role":"symbol","title":"MLNSymbolStyleLayer","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"},{"type":"text","text":" is a style layer that renders icon and text labels"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"at points or along lines on the map."}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnsymbolstylelayer","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNSymbolStyleLayer"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNSymbolStyleLayer/symbolPlacement":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/symbolPlacement","role":"symbol","title":"symbolPlacement","abstract":[{"text":"Label placement relative to its geometry.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnsymbolstylelayer\/symbolplacement","fragments":[{"text":"symbolPlacement","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"}}}